(1, '2014-09-04 21:45:57', '2014-09-09 02:36:08', 'Fall Letter Template', '<p style="text-align: center;">{{logo}}</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;"><strong>Dear {{first-name}} {{last_name}},</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">Congratulations! This letter is an invitation to participate in the <strong>{{camp_year}} {{season}} Nike Blue Chip @{{graduation_year}} Lacrosse Camp.</strong>If you accept this invitation, please visit the link, where you will be directed to enter your personal information and fill out medical and release forms: <strong>{{token}}</strong> (*This link is a one-time use link; if you encounter any issues, please contact us for assistance at sailinshoe3@comcast.net).</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">The&nbsp;<strong>{{camp_year}} &nbsp;{{season}} Nike Blue Chip Lacrosse Camp</strong> will be held on&nbsp;Saturday, November 22nd and Sunday, November 23rd at the Mecklenburg County Sportsplex at Matthews in Charlotte, NC.&nbsp;Games will take place on Saturday, November 22 beginning at 9am and ending by 6pm and on Sunday, November 23 beginning at 8am and ending by 2pm.&nbsp;The Sportsplex is located about 30 minutes from Charlotte Douglas International Airport (CLT). All players must provide their own transportation, lodging, and meals.&nbsp;Please go to <strong>lacrossecamp.com</strong> for more information about lodging and online store.</span></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">Each player&rsquo;s profile will be in a booklet given to the coaches in attendance. Upon arrival, each player will be provided with his own numbered reversible jersey, which will be listed in the coach&rsquo;s booklet. Unfortunately, team requests cannot be honored. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">The cost of the <strong>Nike Blue Chip Lacrosse Camp</strong> is $500.00. This payment is <strong>non-refundable (in the case of an injury, a 50% refund will be given to those who present a note from a physician before November 1). </strong> If we do not receive your payment by {{payment_due_date}}, your spot will be forfeited and another player will be chosen to take your place. Please enclose your confirmation letter along with a check made payable to Maryland Lacrosse Academy Inc. and mailed to the following address (regular US mail only, do not send mail signature required):&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Nike Blue Chip Lacrosse Camp <br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3302 Foster Ave. <br /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Baltimore MD 21224&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">\r\n<p>If you have any questions please email me at sailinshoe3@comcast.net <br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Sincerely,</p>\r\n<p>Jake Reed</p>\r\n<p>Nike Blue Chip Lacrosse Camp</p>\r\n</div>', NULL),
(2, '2014-09-05 01:06:39', '2014-09-09 02:23:20', 'Summer Letter Template', '<div class="center small_logo"><img src="images/bluechip_logo.png" alt="logo" /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;"><strong>Dear {{first-name}} {{last_name}},</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">Congratulations! This letter is an invitation to participate in the <strong>{{camp_year}} {{season}} &nbsp;Nike Blue Chip {{graduation_year}} Lacrosse Camp.</strong> If you accept this invitation, please visit this link, where you will be directed to enter your personal information and fill out medical and release forms: <strong>{{token}}</strong> (*This link is a one-time use link; if you encounter any issues, please contact us for assistance at sailinshoe3@comcast.net).</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">The&nbsp;<strong>{{camp_year}} &nbsp;{{season}} Nike Blue Chip Lacrosse Camp</strong>&nbsp;will be held on&nbsp;Saturday, November 22nd and Sunday, November 23rd at the Mecklenburg County Sportsplex at Matthews in Charlotte, NC.&nbsp;Games will take place on Saturday, November 22 beginning at 9am and ending by 6pm and on Sunday, November 23 beginning at 8am and ending by 2pm.&nbsp;The Sportsplex is located about 30 minutes from Charlotte Douglas International Airport (CLT). All players must provide their own transportation, lodging, and meals.&nbsp;Please go to&nbsp;<strong>lacrossecamp.com</strong>&nbsp;for more information about lodging and online store.</p>\r\n<p style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: medium;">Each player&rsquo;s profile will be in a booklet given to the coaches in attendance. Upon arrival, each player will be provided with his own numbered reversible jersey, which will be listed in the coach&rsquo;s booklet. Unfortunately, team requests cannot be honored. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';